                    <div class="name" id="toName">My Dearest</div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <div class="from-label">From</div>
                    <div class="name" id="fromName">Your Love</div>
                </div>
                <div class="click-instruction">Click to open ‚úâÔ∏è</div>
            </div>

            <div class="letter" id="letter">
                <div class="letter-header">
                    <div class="letter-title">üíï My Valentine üíï</div>
                    <div class="letter-subtitle">February 14, 2026</div>
                </div>
                <div class="letter-content">
                    <p>Every moment with you feels like a beautiful dream come true. Your smile brightens my darkest days, and your laughter is the melody my heart dances to.</p>
                    <p>You make every day feel like Valentine's Day, but today I want to make it official...</p>
                    <div class="question">Will you be my Valentine? üíñ</div>
                </div>
                <div class="button-container">
